{"tid":1744034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐懼鳥已被拘捕","createTime":"2019-11-21T13:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T06:06:48.000Z","uid":29969,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bab7967e7500ad43398172aa75fb1013f8e413e9","tid":1744034,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7brehu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7brehu.png&h=de8206b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d5cf081d4bcd86a86179c752a2496a4bc9b1740","tid":1744034,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:23:53.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt825ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=7103bd39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt825ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=090a964e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt825ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=16c432a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"h